de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces

Interface ICustomReport

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface ICustomReport
extends Serializable
    it's possible to generate new reports. The report must be registered at the client. How to use: In the BRule ClientLogin in the function postLogin: de.ityx.mediatrix.client.dialog.util.report.Report.addCustomReport(new TestReport);

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int DEFAULT_ID
      The id is used to create the unique id for the new report.
